Package it.polimi.ingsw.client

Class ModelView

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ModelView
public class ModelView
extends java.lang.Object
This class contains a small representation of the game model, and contains linking to the main client actions, which will be invoked after an instance control.
